Bugs

Bug 1.
# Data race on writing_rollback variable, a part of the force recovery feature recently added.
# If this variable gets messed up, an assert may erroneously fire.
# Fixed on nov2024-update branch

Bug 2.
# SUMMARY: ThreadSanitizer: data race /home/rfp/projects-tokuft/tokuft/portability/os_malloc.cc:283:10 in os_malloc_usable_size(void const*)
# SUMMARY: ThreadSanitizer: data race /home/rfp/projects-tokuft/tokuft/portability/portability.cc:147:20 in toku_os_get_pagesize()
# Sometimes detected with running the locktree tests.
# The locktree tests need to initialize the portability module.

Bug 3.
# toku_ft_adjust_logical_row_count data race.
# The adjust logical row count is racy.  Could use an algorithm that does
# an unsafe read followed by a compare and exchange instead.
# Detected with the thread sanitizer when running ft tests.
# Suppression in the tokuft.tsan.suppressions file.

Bug 4.
# Data race ft_copy_for_checkpoint_unlocked __tsan_memcpy and inject_message
# Detected with the thread sanitizer when running the ft tests.

Bug 5. 
# Lock order inversions on cache file list and pair list.
# Env open write locks cache file list then write locks pair list.
# Begin checkpoint read locks pair list then read locks cache file list.
# Detected when running the ydb tests.
# Simple fix to begin checkpoint to switch lock acquisition order and match the env open order.
# Suppression in the tokuft.tsan.suppressions file.

Bug 6.
# Lock order inversions caused by toku_rollback_dictionary_redirect.  The redirect code
# should always use the same ft ref locking order.
# Detected when running the ydb tests.
# Suppression in the tokuft.tsan.suppressions file.

Bug 7.
# SUMMARY: ThreadSanitizer: data race /home/rfp/projects-tokuft/tokuft/ft/ft.cc:199:47 in ft_checkpoint(cachefile*, int, void*)
# Data race ft_checkpoint and adjust_logical_rows.

Bug 8.
# SUMMARY: ThreadSanitizer: data race /home/rfp/projects-tokuft/tokuft/ft/ft-ops.cc:1690:12 in toku_bnc_should_promote(ft*, ftnode_nonleaf_childinfo*)
# SUMMARY: ThreadSanitizer: data race /home/rfp/projects-tokuft/tokuft/ft/node.cc:646:93 in bn_needs_ancestors_messages(ft*, ftnode*, int, pivot_bounds const&, ancestors*, __toku_msn*)
